/AGMIMG_init_common
{
	currentdict/T known{/ImageType/T ldf currentdict/T undef}if
	currentdict/W known{/Width/W ldf currentdict/W undef}if
	currentdict/H known{/Height/H ldf currentdict/H undef}if
